<div1 type="case">

<pb facs="hc.case.0035.005"/>

<p> County of Saint Louis Ss: </p>

<p> On behalf of William Blackburn <del> the above named petitioner </del> Sarah Broadwater, who makes the foregoing petition 
being duly sworn, says, that the said petition above by her
signed is true in substance &amp; matter of fact to his best 
knowledge &amp; belief &amp; further saith not. </p>

<p> Sarah her X mark Broadwater</p>

<p> Sworn &amp; Subscribed this 10th day of April A.D. 1855 before me. </p>
<p> John W. Colvin Law Com </p>

<p> Filed 11th April 1855 </p>
<p> John W. Colvin </p>

</div1>
    
